      Find existing or create a new sign detail.
      Parameters:
      dt - DMS type.
      p - Portable flag.
      t - Sign technology.
      sa - Sign access.
      l - Sign legend.
      bt - Beacon type.
      hmk - Hardware make.
      hmd - Hardware model.
      smk - Software make.
      smd - Software model.
      st - Supported MULTI tags (bit flags).
      mp - Maximum number of pages.
      ml - Maximum MULTI string length.
      ba - Beacon activation flag.
      ps - Pixel service flag.
      Returns:
      Matching existing, or new sign detail.
